      809ecd4e2868d5630102f20474a2f19385417c38
      Wang Guan &lt;momocraft@gmail.com&gt;
      1372390398 +0900
      merge origin/gh-pages-source: Fast-forward

  %ul(style="list-style-type: none;")
    %li
